name: The Magician
description:
If you came across this card and you bought it, you will be given a solution to your problems, a career going lucky and a love life that will make you happy. You have to trust yourself to get what you need from them.
The meaning of the moon symbol indicates that a wish is on the way and you must not give up for this wish to come true.
If you give up on this wish, you may get painful results as a result of the events that will come your way.
The elixir symbol means that you will get out someone from your life and as a result you will solve some problems. If there are people in your life who make you unhappy and do not support you, you may consider removing them from your life.
When you get your life in order, lucks will come to you quickly.
